Task 8: Color and Background

Color:
- Hex: #FF0000 (red)
- RGB: rgb(255, 0, 0) (red)
- HSL: hsl(0, 100%, 50%) (red)
Background:
- Solid color: background-color: #FF0000;
- Gradient: background: linear-gradient(to right, #FF0000, #00FF00);
- Image: background-image: url('image.jpg');

 Example:
<div style="background-color: #FF0000; color: white;">
    This div has a red background.
</div>

<div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #FF0000, #00FF00);">
    This div has a gradient background.
</div>